String It
by Phil Cote

What It Does:
String It generates a curve that runs though the center or every object selected in a scene.

How to Install It:
1.  Pull up the preferences box and go to add-ons. 
2.  Click install addon and install the string it script.
3.  Go to the "add curves section of the "add-ons" tab.
4.  Check box the "String It Script."
5.  Close the preferences box.

How to Use It:
1.  In the 3D view, select the scene objects you want to have the curve run through.
2.  When done, hit the space bar and type in "String It"
3.  Hit enter.  Your selected objects should all have a curve running through their centers.
